<div class="prose dark:prose-invert mb-12">
  <h2 class="text-center sm:text-start">Publish your writing from your inbox</h2>

  <p>
    Pagecord is a simple, minimalist blogging app managed entirely by email.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-8 text-center not-prose">
    <%= link_to new_signup_path do %>
      <div class="my-2 inline-flex font-semibold p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm text-white bg-bmc-pink">Sign up for free now!</div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-center sm:text-start">How it works</h2>

  <p>
    All you need is an email account. No new tools to wrangle.
  </p>
  <p>
    Write your posts in your email client and send them to your unique
    Pagecord email address. That's it! Your posts will be published automatically.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-center sm:text-start">It's free, but you can pay for fancy features</h2>

  <p>
    Pagecord is <strong>free to use</strong>.
  </p>
  <p>
    It does cost money to keep the lights on. You can help out <%= link_to "by donating", "https://buymeacoffee.com/heyolly" %>, or you can pay for premium features such as images, link unfurling, analytics, email subscriptions and custom domains<sup>*</sup>.
  </p>
  <p>
    <small><sup>*</sup> None of these features exist, but I'll build them if there's demand. Please <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc5AOBhsW_geuGSNjoQaN1luzISJRfaBxhW2tXP31qchPSdNQ/viewform">register your interest</a>!</small>
  </p>

  <div class="mt-12 flex justify-center">
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdnjs.buymeacoffee.com/1.0.0/button.prod.min.js" data-name="bmc-button" data-slug="heyolly" data-color="#FF5F5F" data-emoji="â˜•"  data-font="Cookie" data-text="Donate" data-outline-color="#000000" data-font-color="#ffffff" data-coffee-color="#FFDD00" ></script>
  </div>
</p>
